item.title: The year I was 25
item.description: I dream in POLIWAT First off some sound I have been completely sober for 5 days Tuesday 952 PM At Diridon in San Jose. Hopefully the 17 bus comes and I’ll get to my place in Santa Cruz before midnight. My laptop charging porter burned out while on the train so this is the last charge until I repair it. I found a shop in San Jose that has a new pot I can install myself for 40 bucks.
